<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Scan the start receipt with the BMF receipt validation app</p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">After registering the POS at FinanzOnline, scan the QR code of the start receipt. The app checks if the signature on the POS receipts is valid.<br>
<strong><em>Tip:</em></strong> You need to scan the start receipt within a week after registering the signature card and the POS at FinanzOnline.</p></td>
